    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
        }

        .sidebar {
            height: 100%;
            width: 240px;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #111;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            padding-top: 16px;
        }

            .sidebar a {
                padding: 10px 14px 10px 10px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 20px;
                color: white;
                display: block;
            }

                .sidebar a:hover {
                    color: #ff6a00;
                }

        .main {
            margin-left: 240px; /* Same as the width of the sidenav */
            padding: 0px 10px;
        }

        @@media screen and (max-height: 450px) {
            .sidebar {
                padding-top: 15px;
            }

                .sidebar a {
                    font-size: 18px;
                }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="sidebar">
        <a href="/ShowCase/Index/"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></i> &nbsp; Ana Sayfa </a> @*başında 1 boşluk olması için &nbsp; kullandık*@
